WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:04.853
Consider a scenario where a critical global project is failing.

00:00:05.613 --> 00:00:11.335
The launch is delayed, the budget is bleeding, and the cross-functional team is frustrated.

00:00:11.955 --> 00:00:18.937
The practical payoff of handling this correctly is the difference between a stalled career and transformative leadership.

00:00:19.478 --> 00:00:28.861
When facing a complex, undefined challenge at headquarters, an average manager might react by assigning blame or enforcing rigid rules.

00:00:29.601 --> 00:00:36.947
A transformative leader, however, engineers an environment for active, self-built understanding to solve the root cause.
